Package model.calendar

Class Week

java.lang.Object
model.calendar.Week
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Week extends Object implements Serializable
This class is a representation of a single week in that holds data about 7 days in the week and also the start and the end date of a week period. It implements Serializable interface for persistence purposes.
